data.name: ReadFips1
data.value: select top(1) [STATE], COUNTY, LOCATION, STATE_ABBREVIATION from CKT_FIPS where ([STATE] = @state) and (COUNTY = 000) and (LOCATION = 00)

data.name: ReadFips2
data.value: select top(1) [STATE], COUNTY, LOCATION, STATE_ABBREVIATION from CKT_FIPS where (STATE_ABBREVIATION = @stateAbbreviation) and (COUNTY = 000) and (LOCATION = 00)
